snippet.title: Basingstoke Alpha 3
snippet.description:
So, you wondered what we'd been up to for the last few months? Wonder no more!

This is the current state of Basingstoke. Or at least what we imagine Basingstoke would look like in the not-too-distant future following invasion by our old friends the Titans.

Just like the real Basingstoke of Hampshire,  England, this one seems to be full of patrolling monsters, deadly tentacles grasping from the sewers, and the reanimated undead corpses of all the citizens wiped out by the initial neutron bomb that heralded the start of the invasion.

Nothing a nice kebab can't fix.
